     C* Two DEBUG lines naming different factor-2 output files must be a
     C* hard parse error (manual: "the same output file name must appear
     C* in factor 2 for all DEBUG statements in a program").
     H        1
     FDBGOUT  O   F    80              DISK
     FDBGOUT3 O   F    80              DISK
     C                     DEBUGDBGOUT
     C                     DEBUGDBGOUT3
